foEnabled).isFalse()\n      assertThat(log.isDebugEnabled).isFalse()\n    } finally {\n      Await.result(system.terminate(), 10.seconds)\n    }\n  }\n\n  @Test\n  def slf4jLoggerActorInitializesAndHandlesAllLogEventShapes(): Unit = {"}]}
